This section contains various missions.

## D.R.Ops

Dangerous & Rapid Ops (D.R.Ops) are intended to be short missions that are quick to set-up and run. The descriptions are relatively brief with plenty of room for referee and player improv.

### [PLAY: Protect Latent Australians in Yellow](/Missions/M-PLAY.qmd)

Protect a rendition of The King in Yellow being performed at an outdoor theatre in the Australian outback. Hopefully nothing strange will happen.

## Dilemmas

In the below missions the team has to choose between one of two. Normally, 2 of the factions are up against each other and the team chooses which faction to side with which will determine the mission they ultimately carry out.

### [AVOW: Assassinating the Veiled at the Opulent Wedding](/Missions/M-AVOW.qmd)

Commit or stop the assassination of a Tartarus bride and their Proteus bride during their high profile matrimonies.

### [DEBT: Drug Exchange on a Bridge Tonight](/Missions/M-DEBT.qmd)

Purchase or sell Holy water on a bridge. Hopefully no shenanigans will ensue!

### [POPS: Possible Oil Pipe Sabotage](/Missions/M-POPS.qmd)

Either side with Kraken to prevent an oil pipe sabotage of TAG to do the sabotaging.

## Paranormal events

In the below missions the team will have to investigate and stop a paranormal event. This may involve monster hunting, exploring strange places, or something completely different.

### [AWE: Auroras & Worm Eradications](/Missions/M-AWE.qmd)

A Refraction Sports event may be stopped due to skiers and snowboarders being found eaten by beasts. Found out what's going on and stop it.

### [DELVE: DOT Expedition Leads to Vein Encounters](/Missions/M-DELVE.qmd)

An new entrance to the DOT has opened. Investigate and stop further raids from occurring.

## Bombastic

These missions won't be categorised normally.

## The Primeval Polytheist's Seasonal Schemes

[Dr. Petra Pufferfish](Gaia/Dr_Petra_Pufferfish.qmd) is the Primeval Polytheist.
She plans to control the world with her three lieutenants; [Blanchard](/Proteus/Blanchard_the_hyperborean.qmd) the Hyperborean, Pudding the Ablated, and Mango the Xenolith.
These missions involve stopping their plans for world domination.

### [__Blanchard's Winter__](/Missions/M-Blanchards_winter.qmd)

FIST are hired by the USA and ERA militaries to stop Blanchard's weather machine. An action packed mission involving an underwater escort of Humpback whale weapons platforms to Blanchard's iceberg. This is followed by a ground attack of Blanchard's ice fortress guarded by Cyborg Polar bears. Finally FIST will only find an elevator in the fortress that will take them to Blanchard's real base of operations, the sunken Titanic!
